OL,3,CAssembly must take action to protect
OL,4,Ccommunity sector, union warns
OL,6,FPeople from the community and
OL,7,Fvoluntary sector have gathered to
OL,8,Fprotest at Stormont over a cliff edge
OL,9,Fin funding which could lead to job
OL,10,Flosses.
OL,12,FA trade union has warned that the
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland Assembly must take
OL,14,F"immediate and decisive action" to
OL,15,Faddress a deepening funding crisis
OL,16,Ffacing the community and voluntary
OL,17,Fsector.
OL,19,FUnison said hundreds of workers in the
OL,20,Fsectors face losing their jobs due to
OL,21,Fa reduction in funding.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@_O]
