OL,3,CAssembly must take action to protect
OL,4,Ccommunity sector, union warns
OL,6,FThe UK Shared Prosperity Fund (UKSPF)
OL,7,Fis replaced by the Local Growth Fund
OL,8,Fon April 1.
OL,10,FIn 2023, EU funding to charities and
OL,11,Fcommunity groups in Northern Ireland
OL,12,Ffrom its European Social Fund (ESF)
OL,13,Fwas ended because of Brexit.
OL,15,FIt was replaced by the UKSPF which
OL,16,Fwill in turn be replaced by the Local
OL,17,FGrowth Fund.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
