OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774947927
OL,3,CAssembly must take action to protect
OL,4,Ccommunity sector, union warns
OL,6,FThat new fund has a 70/30 capital-to-
OL,7,Frevenue split, resulting in funding
OL,8,Fcuts to the voluntary and community
OL,9,Fsector.
OL,11,FUnison said the sector is now facing a
OL,12,F"deepening funding crisis".
OL,14,FA statement said: "This sector is a
OL,15,Fvital pillar of support for some of
OL,16,Fthe most vulnerable people in our
OL,17,Fsociety.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@ZO]vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774947927
OL,3,CAssembly must take action to protect
OL,4,Ccommunity sector, union warns
OL,6,F"It delivers essential frontline
OL,7,Fservices that individuals, families,
OL,8,Fand communities rely on every day. Yet
OL,9,Fit is now at breaking point.
OL,11,F"Without urgent intervention, hundreds
OL,12,Fof skilled and dedicated workers face
OL,13,Fthe very real prospect of losing their
OL,14,Fjobs.
OL,16,F"These are not just numbers ` they are
OL,17,Fexperienced professionals whose work
OL,18,Funderpins critical services across
OL,19,Fhealth, social care, and community
OL,20,Fsupport."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
