PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774947927
OL,3,CAssembly must take action to protect
OL,4,Ccommunity sector, union warns
OL,6,FThe union warned that the
OL,7,F"consequences of inaction will be
OL,8,Fsevere".
OL,10,FIt said: "As jobs are lost, services
OL,11,Fwill inevitably be reduced or
OL,12,Fwithdrawn altogether.
OL,14,F"This will leave service users ` many
OL,15,Fof whom are already at significant
OL,16,Frisk ` without the support they need
OL,17,Fto stay safe, well, and connected.
OL,19,F"The impact will be felt most acutely
OL,20,Fby those who can least afford it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@GO]rD@JOUvD@AOU{D@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
